description:
Exposes the following information for use directly from MSBuild, C# and VB:
			GitBranch:            $(GitBranch), ThisAssembly.Git.Branch
			GitCommit:            $(GitCommit), ThisAssembly.Git.Commit
			GitBaseVersion:       $(GitBaseVersion), ThisAssembly.Git.BaseVersion
			GitCommits:           $(GitCommits), ThisAssembly.Git.Commits
			GitTag:               $(GitTag), ThisAssembly.Git.Tag
			GitBaseTag:           $(GitBaseTag), ThisAssembly.Git.BaseTag
			GitVersionMajor:      $(GitVersionMajor), ThisAssembly.Git.Version.Major
			GitVersionMinor:      $(GitVersionMinor), ThisAssembly.Git.Version.Minor
			GitVersionPatch:      $(GitVersionPatch), ThisAssembly.Git.Version.Patch
			GitVersionLabel:      $(GitVersionLabel), ThisAssembly.Git.Version.Label
			GitVersionDashLabel:  $(GitVersionDashLabel), ThisAssembly.Git.Version.DashLabel
summary: Access commit information from MSBuild and C#/VB code
title: Git Info from MSBuild, C# and VB
